data.text:
harem_owners is the Yahoo Group for the leaders of the Nick's Harem faction. The site's banner describes it as "Nick's Harem: Owner's List".

The restricted Group was founded on 5 October 1998. It has 2 members.

Group Description[]

A place for the owners of the Nick's Harem mailing list to discuss business and for new members to send their age statements to.

Group Moderator: harem_owners-owner@egroups.com

To subscribe, send a message to egroups.com-subscribe@harem_owners or go the this Yahoo group's home page at http://groups.yahoo.com/group/harem_owners

Group Website[]

http://foreverknight.amypreed.com

Group Information[]

Members :2

Category: Other

Founded: Oct 5, 1998

Language: English

Group Settings[]

This is a restricted group.

Attachments are permitted.

Members cannot hide email address.

Not listed in Yahoo Groups directory.

Membership requires approval.

Messages are not moderated.

Anyone can post messages.
